// Signing configuration (committed, safe for a public repo).
// The real Apple Development Team ID is NOT stored here — it lives in Local.xcconfig
// (gitignored). Copy Local.xcconfig.example → Local.xcconfig and fill in your team id.
// If Local.xcconfig is absent, DEVELOPMENT_TEAM stays empty and Xcode uses automatic /
// personal-team signing (or prompts), so generation/build never break on a fresh clone.

DEVELOPMENT_TEAM =

#include? "Local.xcconfig"
